{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/title_about.png?t=1719148735\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/gif_walk.gif?t=1719148735\" /><br>Embark on an extraordinary journey to the enigmatic Nawala Island, a remote paradise filled with curious villagers and an even more peculiar cult. Welcome to a 2D adventure like no other, where you'll recruit, befriend, and uncover the secrets of a world that worships &quot;The Great Box&quot; \u2013 a sentient fridge with a mission to end world hunger.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/title_friend.png?t=1719148735\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/gif_talk.gif?t=1719148735\" /><br>To gain the trust of the villagers, you'll need to whip up their favorite dishes. Craft delicious meals, serve them with love, and watch as they join your cause to worship The Great Box. Fulfill missions from both the villagers and the enigmatic cult leader to befriend them!<br><br>Immerse yourself in the bizarre and charming world of The Great Box cult. Unravel the cult's beliefs and objectives as you strive to bring an end to world hunger, all while preserving the island's unique way of life.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/title_decorate.png?t=1719148735\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/gif_decor2.gif?t=1719148735\" /><br>Put your creativity to the test and decorate Nawala Island and your home to your heart's desire. Create a tranquil haven that reflects your cult's vision and showcases your unique style.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/title_explore.png?t=1719148735\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/gif_explore.gif?t=1719148735\" /><br>Traverse the lush landscapes and vibrant villages of Nawala Island, a place as mysterious as it is beautiful. Every corner holds a new discovery, and every character has a story to tell. As you delve deeper into the island's lore, you'll uncover hidden mysteries that will challenge your understanding of The Great Box, the villagers, and the true purpose of your journey.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2452290?t=1719148735","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1719148735","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1719148735","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1719148735","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/title_about.png?t=1719148735\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452290/extras/gif_walk.gif?t=1719148735\" /><br>Embark on an extraordinary journey to the enigmatic Nawala Island, a remote paradise filled with curious villagers and an even more peculiar cult. Welcome to a 2D adventure like no other, where you'll recruit, befriend, and uncover the secrets of a world that worships &quot;The Great Box&quot; \u2013 a sentient fridge with a mission to end world hunger.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai